| Flask-WTF      | CSRF protection                  |
| Werkzeug       | Password hashing                 |
| scikit-learn   | ML models (Random Forest, LR)    |
| pandas         | Data manipulation                |
| numpy          | Numerical operations             |
| joblib         | Model serialization              |

